---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Detail View"
	description="Clip Detail is where you edit note content, shape sounds, and manage per-clip controls."
>
	<div class="detail-page">
		<header class="detail-header">
			<p class="detail-section-label">Manual</p>
			<h1>Detail View and Clip Detail</h1>
			<p class="detail-lead">
				Clip Detail is where you edit note content, shape sounds, and manage per-clip controls.
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="detail-section">
			<figure class="manual-media" data-wrap="right">
				<img
					src="/images/application-screenshots/detail.png"
					alt="Pooly Clip Detail view showing voice controls and drum clip slots."
					width="686"
					height="1029"
					loading="lazy"
				/>
				<figcaption>
					Clip Detail on an instrument track: edit voice parameters and clip content in one place.
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>
				If you are learning this part of Pooly, start with these sections:
			</p>
			<ul class="detail-links">
				<li>
					<a href="/manual/core-concepts/#16-detail-view">1.6 Detail View</a> for the editing
					model and panel layout.
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/manual/views/clip-launcher/">3 Clip Launcher</a> for how clips open into
					Detail View from the grid.
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/manual/views/browser/">2 Browser</a> for how instrument and effect browsing
					works inside Clip Detail.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<p class="back-link"><a href="/manual/">&larr; Back to Manual</a></p>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.detail-page {
		max-width: var(--content-max);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md);
	}

	.detail-header {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
	}

	.detail-section-label {
		font-size: var(--text-xs);
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
	}

	.detail-header h1 {
		font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 5vw, var(--text-3xl));
		margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
	}

	.detail-lead {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		color: var(--color-text-soft);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.detail-section {
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.detail-section::after {
		content: "";
		display: block;
		clear: both;
	}

	.detail-section p {
		max-width: 46rem;
		color: var(--color-text-soft);
		text-wrap: pretty;
		overflow-wrap: anywhere;
	}

	.detail-links {
		margin-top: var(--space-md);
		padding-left: var(--space-xl);
		max-width: 46rem;
	}

	.detail-links li {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
		color: var(--color-text-soft);
	}

	.back-link {
		margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
		padding-top: var(--space-xl);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
	}
</style>
